        type: "text",
        content:
          "Views from Seminar\n\nCASCFEN, Baku, 20.06.2017 – The Central Asian and Southern Caucasian Freedom of Expression Network (CASCFEN) has conducted one more seminar in the framework of the project titled “Optimization of relations of education workers with media”. The seminar, which was attended by 25 teachers, was conducted in Kurdamir city school No: 3.\n\nThe Principle of the school Bayram Jafarov welcoming the guests noted that the Government of Azerbaijan pays great contribution to the citizen`s enlightenment.\n\nA chairman of CASCFEN and expert of the project Azer Hasret thanked the Azerbaijan state and State Council to Support NGOs under the President of the Republic of Azerbaijan.",
