        type: "text",
        content:
          "Tartar, CASCFEN, 29.07.2013 – The Central Asian and Southern Caucasian Freedom of Expression Network (CASCFEN) has conducted a seminar on July 28, 2013 in Tartar city within the framework of the project titled “Freedom of Expression Culture Dissemination” supported with grant from the NGO Support Council of Azerbaijan. The moderator of the seminar, the Project leader Rey Karimoglu has informed participants about the Project.",
